00179     private int yy_advance()
00180             throws java.io.IOException {
00181         int next_read;
00182         int i;
00183         int j;
00184 
00185         if (yy_buffer_index < yy_buffer_read) {
00186             return yy_buffer[yy_buffer_index++];
00187         }
00188 
00189         if (0 != yy_buffer_start) {
00190             i = yy_buffer_start;
00191             j = 0;
00192             while (i < yy_buffer_read) {
00193                 yy_buffer[j] = yy_buffer[i];
00194                 ++i;
00195                 ++j;
00196             }
00197             yy_buffer_end = yy_buffer_end - yy_buffer_start;
00198             yy_buffer_start = 0;
00199             yy_buffer_read = j;
00200             yy_buffer_index = j;
00201             next_read = yy_reader.read(yy_buffer,
00202                     yy_buffer_read,
00203                     yy_buffer.length - yy_buffer_read);
00204             if (-1 == next_read) {
00205                 return YY_EOF;
00206             }
00207             yy_buffer_read = yy_buffer_read + next_read;
00208         }
00209 
00210         while (yy_buffer_index >= yy_buffer_read) {
00211             if (yy_buffer_index >= yy_buffer.length) {
00212                 yy_buffer = yy_double(yy_buffer);
00213             }
00214             next_read = yy_reader.read(yy_buffer,
00215                     yy_buffer_read,
00216                     yy_buffer.length - yy_buffer_read);
00217             if (-1 == next_read) {
00218                 return YY_EOF;
00219             }
00220             yy_buffer_read = yy_buffer_read + next_read;
00221         }
00222         return yy_buffer[yy_buffer_index++];
00223     }

00288     private int[][] unpackFromString(int size1, int size2, String st) {
00289         int colonIndex = -1;
00290         String lengthString;
00291         int sequenceLength = 0;
00292         int sequenceInteger = 0;
00293 
00294         int commaIndex;
00295         String workString;
00296 
00297         int res[][] = new int[size1][size2];
00298         for (int i = 0; i < size1; i++) {
00299             for (int j = 0; j < size2; j++) {
00300                 if (sequenceLength != 0) {
00301                     res[i][j] = sequenceInteger;
00302                     sequenceLength--;
00303                     continue;
00304                 }
00305                 commaIndex = st.indexOf(',');
00306                 workString = (commaIndex == -1) ? st : st.substring(0, commaIndex);
00307                 st = st.substring(commaIndex + 1);
00308                 colonIndex = workString.indexOf(':');
00309                 if (colonIndex == -1) {
00310                     res[i][j] = Integer.parseInt(workString);
00311                     continue;
00312                 }
00313                 lengthString =
00314                         workString.substring(colonIndex + 1);
00315                 sequenceLength = Integer.parseInt(lengthString);
00316                 workString = workString.substring(0, colonIndex);
00317                 sequenceInteger = Integer.parseInt(workString);
00318                 res[i][j] = sequenceInteger;
00319                 sequenceLength--;
00320             }
00321         }
00322         return res;
00323     }
